    "This also motivated authors to study physiological signals in combination with visual and acoustic modalities.",
    "For example, a study [89] exploited facial expressions and physiological responses such as heart rate and pupil diameter for emotion detection, using an extreme learning machine algorithm.",
    "However, the setup required for measuring the physiological signals makes it infeasible for practical applications.2.3.6.2 Employing deep learning for CMER Due to the growing performance of deep learning algorithms, CMER's focus has greatly shifted to employing deep learning architectures.",
